 like this, but also really exciting. I’ve come a long way, and I’m proud of that.</p><p>And I just want to say thank you. Genuinely. To everyone who’s followed, supported, interacted, or just quietly stuck around, it means more to me than I can really put into words. You’ve all been a part of this in your own way, and I appreciate it so much.</p><p>Here’s to continuing the journey, growing even more, and sharing it all along the way. I’m not stopping anytime soon 💖</p></p>","content":"<p><figure class=\"tmblr-full\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/adc0c762957729bec982664313932607/e55c37197f0bbf9d-12/s640x960/de7d3f2334ff2c0664fc9f0e8c6ff50ab429f87c.jpg\" alt=\"image\" class=\"\"/></figure><figure class=\"tmblr-full\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d5ea0ac2da8b886faf37c245575ea6f2/e55c37197f0bbf9d-9c/s640x960/9c1f36f53c2aab6dd4bd25df252d520cd5e84643.jpg\" alt=\"image\" class=\"\"/></figure><p>So&hellip; it&rsquo;s finally that time, we made it! I&rsquo;m officially at 18 months, and I&rsquo;m so happy to finally be here and share my progress photo with you all. This journey has meant so much to me, and being able to look back and see how far I&rsquo;ve come feels honestly surreal.</p><p>For anyone new here, hi, this is me Terra the face behind the account. It feels a little nerve-wracking putting myself out there like this, but also really exciting. I&rsquo;ve come a long way, and I&rsquo;m proud of that.</p><p>And I just want to say thank you. Genuinely. To everyone who&rsquo;s followed, supported, interacted, or just quietly stuck around, it means more to me than I can really put into words. You&rsquo;ve all been a part of this in your own way, and I appreciate it so much.</p><p>Here&rsquo;s to continuing the journey, growing even more, and sharing it all along the way. I&rsquo;m not stopping anytime soon &#128150;</p></p>","is_root_item":true},{"blog":{"name":"seraphina-aureline","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":3840,"header_full_height":